      "updated": 1773023690457,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "消息流向:\n\n1️⃣ 客户端 → Gateway\n   (HTTP/WS/RPC)\n\n2️⃣ Gateway 分发:\n   • 协议校验\n   • Agent 执行\n   • 插件调用\n   • 渠道路由\n\n3️⃣ 外部服务交互",
      "fontSize": 14.333333333333334,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "消息流向:\n\n1️⃣ 客户端 → Gateway\n   (HTTP/WS/RPC)\n\n2️⃣ Gateway 分发:\n   • 协议校验\n   • Agent 执行\n   • 插件调用\n   • 渠道路由\n\n3️⃣ 外部服务交互",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b1F",
      "autoResize": true
